Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:09.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Ryuugamine Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:10.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:12.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it really you, Kida-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:14.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There aren't as many color gang members as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:18.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Most of them got arrested for starting a gang war in Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:19.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Sonohara Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:22.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:23.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Harima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry! I thought you were someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:27.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you pledge to be a bona fide Ikebukuronian,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:29.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you will overcome this ordeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I found...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:32.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:12.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll give it back! So please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:18.95,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:40.59,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm really pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:46.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my fault, Selty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all because I accepted such a stupid job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:52.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The job itself was supposed to be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:56.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But then that thing just appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You are not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Monster! Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You heard voices from your wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.72,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They called me a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They could have at least called you a "devil woman" or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:24.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell was that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.98,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do I do if it's an alien?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:32.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Selty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:35.13,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Am I supposed to laugh about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:39.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:43.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:51.53,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Apparently, this city is made of jokes, coincidences, and whims.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:05.23,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This situation might be a result of God's whims, or maybe it's just one of his jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:09.22,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I fell in love at first sight with 37 girls during the opening ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:12.23,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and even though I'm going home with the bespectacled girl that's in my top five,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:16.65,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}because of some development that would put soap operas to shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.18,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the mood's ruined by some dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.37,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Screw this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:23.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was pretty hectic last time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:25.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.38,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This ain't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dude, you really surprised me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't expect you to take the initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.13,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\t(855,1606,\c&HF7F7F7&\3c&HF7F7F7&\4c&HF7F7F7&)}No way! Mikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But in the end, you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:49.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wouldn't have wasted such an opportunity if I were in your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:53.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By now, we'd be in WGP talking so romantically about love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So please go out with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:57.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... I—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:01.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nah, you don't have to reply right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm waiting on a reply from seven other girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and I'm trying to make up my mind on who to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:08.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sonohara-san, you don't have to take him seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll just wear yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:13.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Plus he talks like a big playboy, but he's really just a peanut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:14.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even when he hits on girls—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Mikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:22.58,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This guy, known as Ryuugamine Mikado, is my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:25.17,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's only been a couple of days since he came to Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:29.08,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's an honest, naïve guy with an unexpected stubborn side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.18,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thus, I just can't leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.89,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And I'm stuck in a love triangle with this pure-hearted boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.94,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this what they call "youth"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:41.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You two seem to get along pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're so close we're inseparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.36,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To explain this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.58,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have to go back to the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:56.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Yagiri Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:57.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:02.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take your seat, Yagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:07.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think I'll be able to come to school for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:10.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nah, perhaps I'll never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:15.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to take care of something very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't deal with you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:19.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hey, Yagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:27.20,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought, "There are so many weirdos running around,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.53,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yagiri! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.24,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}when Mikado told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.80,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was literally the moment when I fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:37.54,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My heart gave a big ba-dump when I saw her cute smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.71,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh wait, she didn't smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:54.95,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And thus she claimed the top spot of my "girls I'm gonna make my girlfriend" list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:55.68,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Sonohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you heading home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.36,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Say, Sonohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:17.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You aren't in trouble, or getting bullied, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:17.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:20.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come talk to me if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:23.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh yeah, Harima still hasn't come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You two were in the same class back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:35.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It wasn't easy to get you two in the same class here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:40.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your junior high teacher, Saitou-sensei, told me to take good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you don't have to be polite with me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:46.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh yeah, I'll give you a ride home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:47.98,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:51.05,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There was another slasher incident in Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whoa, Nasujima-sensei, is that sexual harassment I see there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:01.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wowzers! You even made the timid, pure, bespectacled class rep moan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:05.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is literally sexual harassment, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:08.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or with a Russian accent, "Sexy kharasho"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:10.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cut that out, Kida!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:13.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sonohara, don't get the wrong idea and start silly rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.96,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does she look like such a frivolous girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, she doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, you have to tone your jokes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:24.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No worries. I'll be the one spreading the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.56,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess I was like a Champion of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.28,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shit, that was so cool of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.29,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's so gonna be head-over-heels for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:35.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kida-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sonohara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:39.62,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice fucking timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:45.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, you should really watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.68,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Most of the rumors about Nasujima are just that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but it's true that he went after a student:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:03.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A sophomore named Niekawa Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:05.96,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She transferred out during second semester last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:10.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People almost found out that she was dating Nasujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:14.37,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's unknown if she made the decision herself, if she was threatened by Nasujima,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:17.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}or if the school forced her to transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, if anything happens, Mikado and I will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:21.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right, Mikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I still don't really get the whole story,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:28.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I'll do anything to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:28.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:33.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're supposed to say, "I'll make the impossible possible with the power of love."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Otherwise you're not a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:36.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.13,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's an oxymoron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:39.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's just appropriate in that situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That aside, about the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Those bullies went to the same junior high as you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, that's what it sounded like from your conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:52.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In junior high, someone with authority was helping you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:56.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but since that person's gone now, they started bullying you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:01.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You still can't find your missing friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:04.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Harima Mika-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:11.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not that she's been absent,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:14.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but she never went home until the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, isn't that something for the cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:21.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She texted me, and she also told her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:25.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It said, "I'm taking a little trip to relax. Please don't worry about me."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A trip to relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:29.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can you listen without getting shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:36.22,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everything in the past few days has made me immune to any kind of shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Harima-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}is a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:43.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:46.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So the guy you were badgering with questions the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's the one being stalked—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:53.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, rather, Mika-chan, who wanted to be loved by him but was rejected, took a trip to forget her bitter experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:57.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's best to leave it to her family to handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If things get worse, they'll call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:04.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Were you two good friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.18,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's up with that question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, we were always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.90,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's pretty sharp when it comes to certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:17.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm really clumsy, and not sociable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:21.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it was always Mika-san that helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She went as far as going to the same school as I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and it felt very awkward for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:33.05,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"She didn't want to let go of you because you made her look better."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:35.93,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if you think that, you shouldn't say it out loud, Mikado-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:41.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That I was just being used by Mika-san to make herself look better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:45.03,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I was using her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:47.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's easier to depend on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:50.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't think I'd be able to live if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:56.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I don't think I need her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.95,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:01.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I decided to be the class representative
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:05.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}just because she wanted to do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought, "At least I can do it in her stead."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought, "I can surpass her if I become class rep."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:16.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm so despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:20.59,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think it's even more despicable to tell other people about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:25.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It sounds like you're asking for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:29.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Surpassing her is the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:34.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, why don't you face it straight up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.98,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}E-Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:43.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:47.83,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really like this part of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:53.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.36,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:01.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? The strongest in Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:03.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:04.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you a journalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean by "strongest"? It sounds so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:09.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, the strongest is the guy on the black bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:10.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I've heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The headless one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:15.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, and then there's the slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:21.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But the strongest in this city would be the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:22.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}Yes, Dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}My home's the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}Thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}Bye-bye, Anri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:36.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think Yagiri-kun and Mika are together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The victim and the stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:41.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like Yagiri-kun has been kidnapped by his stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:42.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Searching for someone, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:45.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:46.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She said it was fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:50.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess it's impossible to find them without the help of an organization or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:56.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikado... You aren't thinking about joining them, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:58.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.22,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The foolishness of youth makes people join color gangs,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:05.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and then they end up regretting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:08.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, but we're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:16.44,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was really depressed before Mikado came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:22.44,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can be this cheerful thanks to a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.55,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Including Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:30.55,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He was innocent when he came here, so the heated atmosphere of this city is getting to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.17,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It pains me to see him acting so cautiously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:35.53,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I could splash some water on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:40.08,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but when I see the glimmer in his eyes, I just can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:43.75,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I'm trying to spend as much time as I can with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:49.57,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I could, I'd do anything to prevent him from getting near the dark side of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.55,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:54.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:03.42,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...swore never to go back there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.71,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is someone spamming the channel with crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.04,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sounds like an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.25,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe he's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.59,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:49.38,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I mean the "haha hahas."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:52.64,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I'm not saying aliens are scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tsumiuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:57.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or Zaika?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Wealth"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll take a look at it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, you've got a job, Selty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:06.96,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's from Shiki-san of the Awakusu Group again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not a very pleasant job though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:12.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Another delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.22,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:17.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, you have to get the stolen goods back first though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have no idea what the goods are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:22.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think it's better not to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:23.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, about the goods...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:28.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The thief's on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:32.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have an idea on his location, so we should be able to corner him easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:34.95,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:41.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The slasher has been quite active lately, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The slasher?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:44.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:47.05,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like he appeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:49.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He just slashes people without killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:52.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, you can't call him the strongest then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The strongest in this city would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Simon from Russia Sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:17:00.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about the informant that moved to Shinjuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Orihara Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:04.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then it has to be that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Heiwajima Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The strongest color gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dude, it's the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They don't have a color.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:17.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Those peeps in yellow were the big shots until last year though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:18.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:20.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, the Yellow Napkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:25.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I heard that they fought the Blue Squares last year, and they wrecked each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:29.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dude, I heard they revived recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't stop the orders from comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:37.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Engawa and scallops are really cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.41,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Speaking of which, haven't they stuck out too much recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The yellow guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, so you noticed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:43.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By yellow, you don't happen to mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:44.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yellow Snapkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You mean "Yellow Napkins."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yep, yep, them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:48.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was Hermes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:53.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, they were annihilated in the fight with the Blue Squares.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:55.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:57.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard their boss went AWOL.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Could you tell me about the Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:11.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One of my friends wants to join them, and I want to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you asking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no one else I can ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:21.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He can't just go to Orihara Izaya obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:28.98,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't know that much about them either,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:31.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but we'll tell you everything we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.82,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sometimes I feel like I'm getting sucked in by this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:40.16,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But Mikado, I won't let you go to that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:56.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:58.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That won't work, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:05.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're Yellow Napkins, ya see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:07.95,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yagiri-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:11.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not Harima Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:18.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know who you are, but please don't get in the way of our elopement of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:21.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elopement of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:22.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you guys really from the Yellow Napkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:44.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't that obvious, Sherlock?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm asking because I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:48.22,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You fucking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:50.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}K-Kida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.13,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh man, Mikado-kun... Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:05.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:08.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sheesh dude, stop worrying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:45.93,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Perhaps I'm the one relying on him in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:51.43,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ever since Mikado came here, I've felt that my bravado is actually becoming more than just show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:57.84,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe this time I can meet her without running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:58.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.46,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's what I really think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:06.19,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't think you'd come,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:09.95,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:10.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He visits me from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:33.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:38.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruna, did you eat already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:39.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:51.33,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, I blacklisted that spammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:53.08,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like it's gonna be peaceful here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.75,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:59.25,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh yeah. I heard that some of the Yellow Napkins \N\Ngot their asses kicked by the slasher yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:01.17,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who are the Yellow Napkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:03.50,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder if the slasher is a henchman of the Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:05.05,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.01,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like this might turn into a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:12.15,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Things that happen in this city might seem unrelated at first glance,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:14.17,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I'm sure there's a link somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:18.98,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe this city holds a distorted reality that's beyond our ability to fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:20.19,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:23.72,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:27.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}G-Good morning, Sonohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.24,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just realized this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.24,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:33.63,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I really like our relationship the way it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:35.99,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One day I'll connect the dots,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:39.13,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and unveil the picture that's currently invisible to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:43.89,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I believe that our relationship will stay the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:16.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:18.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}Well, I can't say much about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.13,0:24:23.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}Anyway, let me fill you in about the details of the now-legendary Kaztano Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.69,0:24:25.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}Next time: On the Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:30.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}However, do not call me "Dotachin."
